  "description": "A close-up, overhead shot showcases a collection of vibrant, translucent glass beads filling a shallow, circular tray. The beads come in a variety of colors including red, orange, yellow, green, blue, and purple. Each bead appears to be slightly irregular in shape and size, catching the light and creating highlights. The beads are densely packed, obscuring much of the tray's bottom. The tray itself appears to be clear, possibly made of plastic or glass. The background is out of focus, showing a grainy texture that seems to be a paved surface.",
